^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|This was actually quite an interesting hand. First the auction. Should Fred bid over 2S? I know it is hard to resist bidding with 18 points  and we have found a fit, so it is likely E/W has a fit as well. However, there is a case to be made for passing. Although bidding could work as well. Fred has some good defense and has some hope of beating 2S. In fact, it turns out we are down 1. Additionally, partner has not raised either of Fred's suit. So it is very probable at best they have an 8 card heart fit, or else partner has long diamonds and chose not to bid.|
