nt||cp|8|AT|^B@2^Y@3^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|This was an interesting auction, and I learned something about playing 2-way Stayman. As I said, if Ally just had a non-invitational hand with spades, she bids 2H to transfer to spades. So, by bidding Stayman and then showing 5 spades, she is showing 10 or 11  and since I have a maximum I should bid 3NT--for weak NT of course.  I always make 3 once Fred returns a diamond. |
